，事故视频显示...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024 /11/15/24297248/cruise-robotaxi-criminal-fine-falsify-report-pedestrian&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/15/24297248/cruise-robotaxi-criminal-fine-falsify-report-pedestrian" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/15/24297248/cruise-robotaxi-criminal-fine-falsify-report-pedestrian</id><author><name>奥马尔·沙基尔</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-11-15T11:11:21-05:00</published><updated> 2024-11-15T11:11:21-05:00</updated><title>最好的扫地机器人</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src =“https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/-QIaz1XovoAhIWqxr6yhdXW0qmA=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x 873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/70693925/Robot_Vacuums_Best_2024.8.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;扫地机器人只会变得越来越好，拥有新的拖地技能、更好的导航功能和更多的自动化程度，这意味着您的工作量会减少。我们挑选了您现在可以购买的最佳机器人。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/22997597/best-robot-vacuum-cleaner&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a >; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/22997597/best-robot-vacuum-cleaner" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/22997597/best-robot-vacuum-cleaner</id><author><name>詹妮弗·帕蒂森·图伊</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-11-15T10:58:52-05:00</published><updated> 2024-11-15T10:58:52-05:00</updated><title> Facebook 正在将其主要指标改为“浏览量”</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;显示由蓝色圆圈包围的 Facebook 徽标的图像&quot; src =“https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/qNh3dcb7Rpsprx4O2uWz4MfGq3o=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn .vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73725433/STK040_VRG_Illo_N_Barclay_1_facebook.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Nick Barclay / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;A7lg9D&quot;>;Facebook &lt;a href=&quot;https://creators.facebook.com/introducing-views-to- simple-content&quot;>;正在将“观看次数”作为衡量内容性能的主要指标，使其&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/7/24215398/instagram-primary-metric-views&quot;>;与 Instagram 指标一致&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;hHY9Ff ”观看次数不仅会根据视频内容进行衡量，还会根据照片、文字帖子等进行衡量。当 Instagram 负责人 Adam Mosseri &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.instagram.com/reel/C-X7FtePYyj/&quot;>;宣布&lt;/a>;今年夏天转向浏览量时，他表示，在整个平台上拥有一个一致的指标将使创作者更容易了解他们的内容的表现。对于卷轴，观看次数是视频播放的次数。对于其他所有内容，视图是指一段内容在用户屏幕上显示的次数，如果同一用户多次查看该内容，则每个实例都算作一次视图。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;dFY2y2&quot; >;Meta 还为帖子&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/9/24152926/threads-view-count-feature-now-available&quot;>;添加了观看次数&lt;/a>;在线程，说这是一个...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/15/24297255/facebook-metrics-views-instagram&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip; &lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/15/24297255/facebook-metrics-views-instagram" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/15/24297255/facebook-metrics-views-instagram</id><author><name>佐藤米娅</name></author></entry></feed>